    Description of data source

    This dataset is from https://www.kaggle.com/henslersoftware/19560-indian-takeaway-orders. The set used has ~74000 rows containing information about an Indian restaurantâ€™s order history from 01-09-2015 to 12-07-2019.

    Each row represents one order of one item. The columns included are order number, date ordered, item name, item price, quantity of item ordered, and total products in order.
